---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="FAQs - Answers on Ideas to Loved Products Process" description="Common questions about our services: from product development and 3D printing to branding and public art. Learn how we turn your ideas into functional, adored realities.">


  <section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="section-title mb-6">
        <span class="gradient-text">FREQUENTLY</span> ASKED QUESTIONS
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
       Common questions about our services, and answers on how we turn your Ideas into loved products.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
<!-- FAQ / Services Questions Section – Exact Visual Match -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header for each service block – bold, centered, service name in blue -->
    
    <!-- 1. PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT -->
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-center mb-10 md:mb-14
        text-gray-900
      ">
        PRODUCT <span class="text-blue-600">DEVELOPMENT</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            DO YOU HELP WITH PROTOTYPING?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we take your concept through prototyping before final production.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            CAN YOU HELP ME LAUNCH MY PRODUCT?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Absolutely! We assist from ideation to market launch.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. WEB DEVELOPMENT -->
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-center mb-10 md:mb-14
        text-gray-900
      ">
        WEB <span class="text-blue-600">DEVELOPMENT</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            CAN YOU MAKE MY WEBSITE RESPONSIVE?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, all our websites are built to work seamlessly on desktop, tablet/iPad and mobile.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            WILL I BE ABLE TO UPDATE MY SITE MYSELF?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We provide CMS options and training if you'd like to make edits on your own.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. GRAPHIC DESIGN -->
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-center mb-10 md:mb-14
        text-gray-900
      ">
        GRAPHIC <span class="text-blue-600">DESIGN</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            WHAT FORMAT WILL I RECEIVE MY FINAL DESIGN?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            You'll receive files in high-resolution formats you may require and mostly Vector Formats (SVG, AI, EPS, PDF).
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            DO YOU PROVIDE REVISIONS?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we include a set number of revisions to ensure you're happy with the design.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. CAD -->
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-center mb-10 md:mb-14
        text-gray-900
      ">
        <span class="text-blue-600">CAD</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            CAN YOU DESIGN A CAR?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we can design car models in CAD, from concept to detailed parts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            WHAT INDUSTRIES DO YOU DESIGN FOR?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We work across automotive, consumer products, architecture and more.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. WOOD CRAFTS -->
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-center mb-10 md:mb-14
        text-gray-900
      ">
        WOOD <span class="text-blue-600">CRAFTS</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            IF I SEE SOMETHING ONLINE LIKE ON ETSY/PINTEREST AND I DON'T AFFORD TO SHIP IT TO RSA ZA, WILL YOU BE ABLE TO DO IT?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we can replicate or customize most designs, depending on legal restrictions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            DO YOU USE SUSTAINABLE WOOD?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We prioritize eco-friendly and sustainably sourced wood for our crafts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 6. 3D PRINTING -->
    <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-center mb-10 md:mb-14
        text-gray-900
      ">
        <span class="text-blue-600">3D PRINTING</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            IS 3D PRINTED STUFF FOOD SAFE?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Most standard 3D printed plastics are not food-safe without special coatings. We can guide you on safe materials.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            WHAT MATERIALS DO YOU USE?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We print in PLA, ABS, PETG and resin depending on your needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 3 -->
        <div class="
          border-4 border-blue-600 rounded-none
          bg-white shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
          p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 col-span-1 md:col-span-2
        ">
          <h3 class="
            text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
            font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 md:mb-6
          ">
            CAN YOU PRINT LARGE OBJECTS?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, large items can be printed in multiple parts and assembled.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Closing CTA Block -->
    <div class="
      mt-16 md:mt-24 lg:mt-32
      bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600
      rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 text-center
      shadow-2xl
    ">
      <h2 class="
        text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl
        font-black tracking-tight leading-none text-white mb-6 md:mb-8
      ">
        CAN'T FIND WHAT YOU'RE<br />
        LOOKING FOR?
      </h2>

      <p class="
        text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl
        text-white/90 font-medium max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8 md:mb-12
      ">
        OUR SPECIALISTS ARE READY TO PROVIDE CUSTOM ANSWERS FOR YOUR UNIQUE<br />
        PROTOTYPES AND DESIGNS.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="
            inline-block bg-white text-pink-600 font-bold
            px-10 py-5 rounded-xl text-lg md:text-xl
            hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-300
            shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl
          "
        >
          START INQUIRY
        </a>

        <a
          href="/services"
          class="
            inline-block bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold
            px-10 py-5 rounded-xl text-lg md:text-xl
            hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300
          "
        >
          VIEW OUR EXPERTISE
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


</MainLayout>
